{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, the search for patterns and significant findings in the data will be conducted to depict a better understanding of Krashen's theory and its relevance in the context of second language learning.",
    "To understand what the acquisition-learning hypothesis entails, we can examine several opinions from experts.",
    "Their views are expressed in different linguistic styles, but have the same meaning in terminology.",
    "The acquisition-learning hypothesis contains two fundamental theories about how people learn languages.",
    "Therefore, there are two language acquisition systems: the acquisition system and the learning system."
  ]
}